1
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:35,710
How did you discover it?

2
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:37,150
I saw a body over there

3
00:00:37,350 --> 00:00:39,210
when I came fishing this morning,

4
00:00:39,350 --> 00:00:40,610
so I called the police.

5
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:42,790
Did you see anyone suspicious around?

6
00:00:42,790 --> 00:00:43,520
No.

7
00:00:58,670 --> 00:00:59,640
I'm sorry.

8
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,660
I don't have the courage
to face legal judgment,

9
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,920
or to confront

10
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:06,560
my former comrades.

11
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:09,200
This is the only way

12
00:01:09,710 --> 00:01:11,230
to end it all.

13
00:01:14,590 --> 00:01:15,640
To be honest,

14
00:01:16,150 --> 00:01:18,680
now that everything
is exposed to the light,

15
00:01:19,789 --> 00:01:22,760
I feel a sense of relief
I've never felt before.

16
00:01:23,789 --> 00:01:26,039
It is time to reveal the truth.

17
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:29,840
The secret buried for ten years

18
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:32,560
can finally be told.

19
00:03:30,710 --> 00:03:31,710
Hello?

20
00:03:32,030 --> 00:03:33,000
Is he awake yet?

21
00:03:35,590 --> 00:03:36,800
Okay. Got it.

22
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,190
Boss.

23
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,520
Wu is out of danger,

24
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,560
but he hasn't woken up yet.

25
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,079
Okay.

26
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:57,079
Request the best possible care
from the bureau.

27
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,030
Let's go over the case again

28
00:04:01,030 --> 00:04:03,240
and see if we can find any new leads.

29
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,030
Come on, Qiao.

30
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:08,710
Liu Zhijun admitted
in the confession letter

31
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:10,360
that his guns
were obtained illegally.

32
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,800
He also admitted
to the shipyard explosion case.

33
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,710
He took bribes from foreign companies

34
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:15,560
to compete with Ma Derong for business,

35
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,560
and orchestrated the plan himself.

36
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:20,120
Including killing Li Hai's wife,
Li Fengxia,

37
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:22,580
hiring Wang Bingkun
to kidnap Hou Shanshan,

38
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:25,950
and attempting on Captain Qin's life.

39
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:27,350
He confessed to all of it.

40
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,190
What about the confession letter?

41
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:33,630
What did Forensics say
about the handwriting analysis?

42
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:34,480
It's his.

43
00:04:36,270 --> 00:04:36,920
Good.

44
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:44,670
Captain Qin,
why would Liu Zhijun commit suicide?

45
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,070
The reason for Liu Zhijun's suicide

46
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,800
is still under investigation.

47
00:04:57,870 --> 00:05:00,200
But I still need
to ask you some questions.

48
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:03,040
Please, go ahead.

49
00:05:06,510 --> 00:05:08,970
What did Liu Zhijun say to you
the day he left?

50
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,560
He just said he was
going on a business trip.

51
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:18,420
He didn't mention anything else.

52
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:21,350
Did you notice anything unusual about him?

53
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,750
Our investigation shows
Liu Feng is studying in the US,

54
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:32,190
living in your private property.

55
00:05:32,190 --> 00:05:33,750
I need you to tell me,

56
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:36,040
given your financial situation,

57
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:38,840
how can you afford
such a lavish lifestyle for him?

58
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,240
Where exactly did your money come from?

59
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:45,790
If you keep hiding the truth,

60
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,480
it will only complicate the case

61
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,630
and put Feng in even more danger.

62
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:53,960
Nothing can happen to Feng.

63
00:05:57,390 --> 00:06:00,720
Captain Qin, Liu Zhijun
definitely didn't commit suicide.

64
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:05,090
What makes you so sure?

65
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:06,960
He called me that day

66
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:09,750
to pack up all the valuable things at home

67
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:11,310
and bring them to him.

68
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,390
If he was planning to kill himself,

69
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:15,870
he wouldn't let me do that.

70
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:22,430
He took the blame for everything,

71
00:06:22,430 --> 00:06:24,270
then committed suicide,

72
00:06:24,270 --> 00:06:25,390
taking with him

73
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:27,510
all his documents and valuables.

74
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:29,720
He obviously wanted to run away.

75
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,000
Right.

76
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,390
Why would he kill himself?

77
00:06:31,390 --> 00:06:32,680
It wasn't suicide.

78
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:35,310
It was murder.

79
00:06:36,310 --> 00:06:37,920
Then who would have a motive?

80
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,870
Let's call it a day.

81
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:44,480
You go take care of Wu.

82
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,600
I'll join you at the hospital later.

83
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,360
Okay.

84
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:58,320
Officer Qin Wen.

85
00:06:59,159 --> 00:06:59,950
I heard

86
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:03,570
Liu Zhijun wrote a confession
before he committed suicide.

87
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,000
The shipyard explosion,

88
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,190
killing Li Fengxia,

89
00:07:06,190 --> 00:07:08,190
hiring someone to kidnap Hou Shanshan,

90
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:09,450
and your car accident.

91
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,190
He did it all.

92
00:07:11,950 --> 00:07:12,680
Why would Liu Zhijun

93
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,410
go to Yulin Bay to kill himself?

94
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,600
What else do you want to say?

95
00:07:19,310 --> 00:07:20,560
Back then, Liu Zhijun

96
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:23,620
was in charge of
fire safety at the shipyard.

97
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,840
He knew the safety hazards
better than anyone.

98
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,270
If Liu Zhijun was silenced,

99
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:32,070
it means someone
worked with him from the inside

100
00:07:32,070 --> 00:07:33,200
to commit the crime.

101
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,570
The shipyard exploded.

102
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:38,130
Ma Derong suffered heavy losses,

103
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,659
but the shipyard didn't go under.

104
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:44,700
Ma Derong could still
call the shots in Nanping.

105
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:46,870
But what happened next?

106
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:48,270
Ma Derong went to prison.

107
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:51,560
Hou Jun used Ma Derong's resources

108
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,240
to start his own business.

109
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,840
Hou Jun was Ma Derong's
trusted aide back then.

110
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:58,360
After Ma Derong went down,

111
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:02,560
he used the connections
and resources he built up

112
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,500
to start his own business.

113
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:05,630
It makes sense.

114
00:08:06,310 --> 00:08:07,240
Trusted aide?

115
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:11,070
I've been by Ma Derong's side
for so many years.

116
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:13,480
I know how to bypass
the forces protecting him

117
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,740
and avoid his network.

118
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:24,990
Have you ever seen a trusted aide

119
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,240
sent his own boss to prison?

120
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:32,809
I just wanted to get rid of
Ma Derong's threat back then.

121
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:37,030
But it seems he wanted
everything Ma Derong had.

122
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:41,240
If that's the case...

123
00:08:54,510 --> 00:08:55,390
Xia Xue.

124
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,790
Where are you?

125
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:58,240
Let's meet.

126
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,150
I just met Qin Wen.

127
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:14,710
Liu Zhijun's death is very suspicious.

128
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:16,480
We analyzed it,

129
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:19,490
and the most suspicious person
right now is Hou Jun.

130
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,120
If I end up in jail,

131
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:28,360
who'd stand to gain the most?

132
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:38,440
Whether Hou Jun is

133
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:41,320
the mastermind
behind the shipyard explosion or not,

134
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,790
you have to take Shanshan

135
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,550
to a safe place now.

136
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:57,240
Did you wash your hands?

137
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,120
Yes, I did.

138
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,320
Let's eat.

139
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,550
Dad.

140
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:10,000
Why didn't you come back yesterday?

141
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,870
I was discussing
a project with Jihai Group.

142
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:12,960
It took all night.

143
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:14,750
Okay. Let's eat.

144
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:15,790
Let's eat.

145
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:21,630
I want to discuss something with you.

146
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,390
Go ahead.

147
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:25,350
I want to transfer Shanshan
to a different school.

148
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,200
Why so sudden?

149
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:28,840
It's just...

150
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,240
What's wrong, Shanshan?

151
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,320
Did you cause trouble again?

152
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:35,320
No.

153
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:38,630
I just want to find a school
with better conditions

154
00:10:38,630 --> 00:10:40,560
and better security for Shanshan.

155
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:42,410
Have you found a suitable one?

156
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:43,320
Yes, I have.

157
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,480
I asked about it today.

158
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:48,410
They said they can
process the paperwork right away.

159
00:10:48,670 --> 00:10:49,670
Is it that urgent?

160
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:53,550
Okay.

161
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:55,790
It's up to you.

162
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:01,910
Dad, eat this.

163
00:11:03,150 --> 00:11:04,480
You're so sweet, honey.

164
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:15,790
I just met Qin Wen.

165
00:11:16,390 --> 00:11:18,590
Liu Zhijun's death is very suspicious.

166
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:20,670
Why didn't you come back yesterday?

167
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,960
I was discussing
a project with Jihai Group.

168
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,960
It took all night.

169
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:49,630
The two of them...

170
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,690
Captain Qin,

171
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:03,030
I've read the files
from Economic Investigation.

172
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:05,230
Before Ma Derong went to prison, Hou Jun

173
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,480
transferred a large sum of assets

174
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,910
into a trust account.

175
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:10,410
Now the account is in Hou Shanshan's name.

176
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:17,510
Is it possible

177
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,840
that before Ma Derong went to prison,

178
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:21,320
the two of them made a deal?

179
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:24,910
Hou Jun would hold
most of the shipyard's assets

180
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,720
to help Ma Derong look after Hou Shanshan

181
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,150
and give her a good life.

182
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:34,200
So after Ma Derong got out,

183
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,660
he wanted the assets back,

184
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,150
but Hou Jun refused.

185
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,790
If Hou Jun wanted to keep the assets,

186
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:43,520
he'd have to make himself the beneficiary.

187
00:13:43,910 --> 00:13:45,150
So what would he do?

188
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:52,840
The kidnapping.

189
00:13:53,270 --> 00:13:53,910
Boss,

190
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,910
is it possible

191
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:58,160
that this kidnapping

192
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:01,670
was planned by Hou Jun himself?

193
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:05,030
Hou Jun used the kidnapping

194
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:08,000
to force Ma Derong to transfer the assets.

195
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:12,280
But this is all just your speculation.

196
00:14:12,630 --> 00:14:14,200
Now Liu Zhijun has taken

197
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,320
all the blame.

198
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:16,510
We have no evidence proving

199
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:18,110
that Hou Jun was behind this.

200
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,370
Careful. Watch your step.

201
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:35,910
What about Taotao if we leave?

202
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:38,080
Dad will take care of Taotao.

203
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:40,150
Isn't Dad coming with us?

204
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:43,440
Dad has other things to do.

205
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:45,630
Then how will he take care of Taotao?

206
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:57,440
Why are you back?

207
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:01,120
If the child leaves now,
she won't be back until the holidays.

208
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,320
I have to see her off.

209
00:15:03,670 --> 00:15:05,070
And check out the school.

210
00:15:05,390 --> 00:15:07,200
If it's not suitable, forget it.

211
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,150
Right?

212
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:10,620
We'll just treat it as a trip to Huacheng.

213
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,840
I'll take her. You go do your work.

214
00:15:17,030 --> 00:15:19,550
Work can be done anytime.

215
00:15:22,510 --> 00:15:23,550
The child,

216
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:26,670
and you,

217
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:30,450
are the most important.

218
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:35,960
Give it to me.

219
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:43,510
Come on.

220
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:46,940
Let's go see the new school, okay?

221
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:47,790
Okay.

222
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:50,030
If it's good,

223
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:51,390
you can study there.

224
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:52,150
If it's not good,

225
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:53,320
we'll come back.

226
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,150
Okay?

227
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:56,670
We'll go play at the amusement park there,

228
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,510
and then have a nice meal.

229
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,550
We offer one-on-one lessons
with experienced

230
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:06,630
foreign teachers here.

231
00:16:06,630 --> 00:16:09,150
We guarantee the child will
pass the language barrier in one semester.

232
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,910
How are the living conditions?

233
00:16:11,150 --> 00:16:12,030
The dormitory area is over there.

234
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:13,390
I'll take you for a tour.

235
00:16:13,390 --> 00:16:14,840
I assure you'll be satisfied
with the conditions.

236
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,150
Wait, just a moment.

237
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:16,910
Excuse me.

238
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,200
Um...

239
00:16:18,910 --> 00:16:20,480
I'm thinking, maybe we should

240
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:22,630
find an apartment for her
near the school.

241
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:25,360
I'll arrange for someone
to come take care of her.

242
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,910
I think this is fine.

243
00:16:28,030 --> 00:16:29,750
They have centralized teaching.

244
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,350
The environment is nice too.

245
00:16:32,390 --> 00:16:34,390
I'm still worried about her safety.

246
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,360
I should still send someone over.

247
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:39,090
No need, it's too much trouble.

248
00:16:43,630 --> 00:16:44,750
You don't need to worry.

249
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:45,600
We have security guards here,

250
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,910
on duty 24 hours a day.

251
00:16:46,910 --> 00:16:49,370
You really don't need
to worry about safety.

252
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,200
Let's listen to the teacher.

253
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:53,970
I'll show you around some more.

254
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,120
You can rest assured.

255
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:58,450
We will take good care of
the child for you.

256
00:16:58,510 --> 00:16:58,910
Okay.

257
00:16:58,910 --> 00:16:59,630
Thank you.

258
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:00,800
You're welcome.

259
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:04,440
Have a safe trip back.

260
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:05,680
Okay, thank you.

261
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:07,310
Bye.

262
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,650
Hello, Mr. Ming.

263
00:17:30,750 --> 00:17:33,550
Xia Xue and Hou Jun
dropped Shanshan off together.

264
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:35,270
They just left.

265
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:38,920
Good. Pick up the child first.

266
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:39,640
Okay.

267
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:50,000
It's for you.

268
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:51,030
Take it.

269
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:53,920
Madam,

270
00:17:54,270 --> 00:17:55,960
this must be kept secret.

271
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:57,200
Don't tell anyone.

272
00:17:58,200 --> 00:18:00,920
I know. Ms. Xia already told me.

273
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:11,680
Does Mom not want me anymore?

274
00:18:15,240 --> 00:18:16,550
Shanshan, you are so cute.

275
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:18,750
How could Mom not want you?

276
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:22,350
By the way, when we get there,

277
00:18:22,350 --> 00:18:23,720
there is an Auntie Xiaoyu.

278
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:27,160
She also wants to play games with you.

279
00:18:27,830 --> 00:18:28,680
Really.

280
00:18:38,750 --> 00:18:41,110
Didn't we agree
that you would leave with Shanshan?

281
00:18:41,110 --> 00:18:44,110
Hou Jun's meeting today
was cancelled unexpectedly.

282
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,550
I don't know why.

283
00:18:45,720 --> 00:18:46,720
I think just to be safe,

284
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:47,920
I'll leave tomorrow.

285
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:50,700
It's better not to arouse his suspicion.

286
00:19:00,270 --> 00:19:02,240
I didn't hand over the DV

287
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:03,750
for another reason.

288
00:19:05,110 --> 00:19:07,030
What does that have to do with me?

289
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:11,000
Your father
died in the shipyard explosion.

290
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:13,700
Does that have nothing
to do with you either?

291
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:33,480
Hello, Shanshan.

292
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:36,720
Hello, Auntie Xiaoyu.

293
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,790
This is from Uncle Chang.

294
00:19:48,110 --> 00:19:48,970
Are you hungry?

295
00:19:49,350 --> 00:19:51,160
I've made lots of delicious food.

296
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,290
Come inside with me.

297
00:20:10,590 --> 00:20:11,310
Come on.

298
00:20:12,510 --> 00:20:13,640
What a feast.

299
00:20:14,590 --> 00:20:16,590
I got inside information today.

300
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:19,170
My collaboration with Jihai Group

301
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:20,720
is a done deal.

302
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:21,590
Here.

303
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:23,550
Let's celebrate.

304
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:26,720
Come on.

305
00:20:28,270 --> 00:20:29,800
Come on. What are you doing?

306
00:20:33,830 --> 00:20:34,960
Stop lying to me.

307
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,400
What's going on?

308
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:42,790
What... What did I

309
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:43,750
lie to you about?

310
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:47,200
Why would I lie to you, Xia Xue?

311
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:53,000
Who did you see Wednesday night?

312
00:20:53,790 --> 00:20:56,160
Wednesday? Didn't I tell you?

313
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,550
I went to see a client.

314
00:20:58,350 --> 00:20:59,270
What client?

315
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:01,880
What client?

316
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:03,510
I see so many people every day.

317
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:04,970
I can't remember clearly.

318
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:15,720
I checked your car's dashcam.

319
00:21:16,070 --> 00:21:17,720
The footage from the 25th is missing.

320
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,110
Where is it? Deleted?

321
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,310
Yes.

322
00:21:23,790 --> 00:21:26,510
I went out with a client on the 25th.

323
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:29,110
They came all this way.

324
00:21:29,350 --> 00:21:31,750
It wouldn't be right
if I didn't treat them well.

325
00:21:31,750 --> 00:21:34,880
Besides, with so much happening lately,

326
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:36,110
I was afraid you'd overthink it,

327
00:21:36,110 --> 00:21:38,350
so I unplugged the dashcam.

328
00:21:38,790 --> 00:21:40,270
What client did you see?

329
00:21:40,830 --> 00:21:41,550
Who was it?

330
00:21:42,070 --> 00:21:43,130
What's their name?

331
00:21:44,350 --> 00:21:45,950
Wait, what's wrong, Xia Xue?

332
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:48,440
Did something happen?

333
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:49,640
Did you really go see a client?

334
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:51,000
Yes, I went to see a client.

335
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,240
Which client?

336
00:21:52,240 --> 00:21:52,960
Do they have a name?

337
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,240
I see so many people every day.

338
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,510
I... I can't remember.

339
00:21:55,510 --> 00:21:56,840
You didn't see a client.

340
00:21:58,350 --> 00:21:59,830
You went to see Liu Zhijun.

341
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:04,160
Why Liu Zhi... where did that come from?

342
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:05,590
Which Liu Zhijun? Tell me.

343
00:22:05,590 --> 00:22:06,790
You don't know him?

344
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:08,030
There are many people named Liu Zhijun.

345
00:22:08,030 --> 00:22:08,550
Which one do you mean?

346
00:22:08,550 --> 00:22:11,160
You came back soaked in rain that night.

347
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:12,350
What kind of client

348
00:22:12,350 --> 00:22:14,550
would you meet
in such heavy rain without an umbrella?

349
00:22:14,550 --> 00:22:17,030
Officer Qin called me the next day,

350
00:22:17,030 --> 00:22:19,090
asked if I had seen a button like this.

351
00:22:20,550 --> 00:22:22,110
Isn't this from your shirt?

352
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:25,240
Why was it at the crime scene?

353
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,130
Do you remember now?

354
00:22:35,440 --> 00:22:36,400
Did you

355
00:22:37,510 --> 00:22:38,590
kill Liu Zhijun?

356
00:23:25,720 --> 00:23:27,310
You came to see me off personally.

357
00:23:27,310 --> 00:23:28,200
Yes.

358
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:29,790
Where is the boat?

359
00:23:29,790 --> 00:23:30,750
There is no boat.

360
00:23:32,470 --> 00:23:33,550
Are you messing with me?

361
00:23:33,550 --> 00:23:35,030
Don't rush, Liu.

362
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:36,440
I want to discuss something with you.

363
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:37,310
At a time like this?

364
00:23:37,310 --> 00:23:38,640
Discuss what?

365
00:23:39,680 --> 00:23:41,810
Let's discuss how you're going to die.

366
00:23:46,030 --> 00:23:47,350
I gave up my promotion back then,

367
00:23:47,350 --> 00:23:50,000
transferred to the Security Department,
then the Public Security Bureau,

368
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:52,550
all because I was afraid
they'd dig up that old case.

369
00:23:52,550 --> 00:23:54,880
And now you want me dead?

370
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:56,680
Don't forget.

371
00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:58,270
Sending Wang Bingkun
to kidnap Hou Shanshan,

372
00:23:58,270 --> 00:23:59,750
luring Ma Derong out,

373
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:00,830
threatening to get the DV tape...

374
00:24:00,830 --> 00:24:02,200
You did all that.

375
00:24:04,550 --> 00:24:06,110
Let's see

376
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:07,790
who ends up dead.

377
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:19,030
Since you think I killed him,

378
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:21,200
why didn't you hand the shirt

379
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:22,880
over to the police?

380
00:24:31,110 --> 00:24:31,920
Xia Xue,

381
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:34,400
this has nothing to do with you.

382
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:36,110
Please, stay out of it, okay?

383
00:24:39,590 --> 00:24:40,440
You admit it.

384
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:44,400
You really have to believe me.

385
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:45,640
Believe you about what?

386
00:24:45,640 --> 00:24:47,030
I did it for you,

387
00:24:47,030 --> 00:24:48,110
for this family,

388
00:24:48,110 --> 00:24:49,110
for us.

389
00:24:55,750 --> 00:24:57,160
You killed for me?

390
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:02,030
I can give the shirt
to the police anytime.

391
00:25:02,030 --> 00:25:03,110
Hou Jun,

392
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:05,170
I just want to hear the truth from you.

393
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:16,570
It's his fault for not
understanding the situation.

394
00:25:23,110 --> 00:25:25,310
He couldn't tell the fish from the bait.

395
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,310
Who's the pawn,

396
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:34,260
and who's really controlling the board.

397
00:25:38,510 --> 00:25:40,590
Then let's see who dies first, you or me.

398
00:25:40,590 --> 00:25:42,790
Figueroa Street,

399
00:25:42,790 --> 00:25:44,720
No. 2722.

400
00:25:47,030 --> 00:25:49,830
It's quite close to
the University of California.

401
00:25:54,790 --> 00:25:56,390
You're usually very stingy,

402
00:25:56,830 --> 00:26:00,160
but you treat your son really well.

403
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:04,350
Dad, save me!

404
00:26:04,790 --> 00:26:06,310
Dad, save me!

405
00:26:06,550 --> 00:26:07,110
Hou Jun.

406
00:26:07,110 --> 00:26:07,960
Dad!

407
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:08,880
Don't do this.

408
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:09,920
Dad, save me!

409
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:10,830
You can't do this.

410
00:26:10,830 --> 00:26:11,830
Your choice.

411
00:26:12,680 --> 00:26:13,590
You die,

412
00:26:14,310 --> 00:26:15,400
or your son dies.

413
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:21,590
Hou Jun,

414
00:26:22,550 --> 00:26:25,550
how did you get here, step by step?

415
00:26:25,550 --> 00:26:28,720
We shouldn't forget our roots, should we?

416
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:30,440
If you hadn't forced me,

417
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:33,790
how would I have gotten here,
step by step?

418
00:26:37,030 --> 00:26:39,000
Mr. Ma, I can't drink.

419
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,860
Let me toast you with tea instead.

420
00:26:42,790 --> 00:26:43,650
You wrote this?

421
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:48,200
Eat it.

422
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:51,030
Mr. Ma is joking with you.

423
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,120
I told you to eat this!

424
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:03,200
You guys keep eating.

425
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:03,640
Eat.

426
00:27:05,270 --> 00:27:06,070
Okay.

427
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:06,680
Eat.

428
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:07,550
Come on.

429
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:39,200
I actually admire what you did today.

430
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:41,130
You endured what others couldn't.

431
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:44,390
You're sure to make something
of yourself one day.

432
00:27:45,790 --> 00:27:48,350
The reason Ma Derong is so successful

433
00:27:48,640 --> 00:27:50,920
is simply because he has money.

434
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:52,850
People are willing to support him,

435
00:27:53,550 --> 00:27:55,720
and they can build their own network.

436
00:27:57,350 --> 00:27:59,110
Once Ma Derong is destroyed,

437
00:27:59,510 --> 00:28:01,590
you, Hou Jun,

438
00:28:01,830 --> 00:28:03,550
can take his place.

439
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,830
So what do you want to do?

440
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:09,240
We can't let those foreign orders
be delivered on time.

441
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:11,110
Why don't we blow up

442
00:28:11,110 --> 00:28:11,970
that shipyard?

443
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:12,880
Blow it up?

444
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:13,400
Yes.

445
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:16,320
Wouldn't that kill people?

446
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,110
Calm down.

447
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:19,790
You're losing it
before the shipyard even blows.

448
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:20,790
Sit down.

449
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:24,400
Who at the top

450
00:28:24,640 --> 00:28:27,200
didn't get there by stepping on others?

451
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:28,270
Tell me.

452
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:30,960
What am I doing?

453
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:33,010
I'm building a ladder for you.

454
00:28:35,750 --> 00:28:37,590
If we don't take down Ma Derong,

455
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:40,030
you and I will always be stepped on,

456
00:28:40,030 --> 00:28:41,830
always be his dogs.

457
00:28:42,310 --> 00:28:43,550
You want that?

458
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:44,880
I don't.

459
00:28:47,590 --> 00:28:48,830
I don't want to be

460
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:51,430
a lowly section chief
at the shipyard forever.

461
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:55,640
Scared?

462
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,270
To achieve great things,

463
00:28:58,830 --> 00:29:00,200
you need guts.

464
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:03,220
Success doesn't just fall into your lap.

465
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:06,790
Loser!

466
00:29:07,270 --> 00:29:08,240
Loser!

467
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:09,640
Loser!

468
00:29:11,110 --> 00:29:12,590
You piece of trash!

469
00:29:12,590 --> 00:29:14,790
You're just a dog I raised!

470
00:29:14,790 --> 00:29:17,680
You have to eat shit if I told you so!

471
00:29:21,510 --> 00:29:23,030
So what do you want me to do?

472
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:29,000
I'll provide the money

473
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,200
and find the people.

474
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:31,400
You handle the contact.

475
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:33,270
Also, get the key to the shipyard's

476
00:29:33,270 --> 00:29:34,480
gas equipment room.

477
00:29:34,790 --> 00:29:35,510
Who's it?

478
00:29:36,550 --> 00:29:37,830
You called me?

479
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,790
Once inside the equipment room,

480
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:50,200
just overload the pressure.

481
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:51,070
The gas valves

482
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:52,330
will definitely leak.

483
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:54,750
Then, all it takes is a spark,

484
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:56,440
and the shipyard will blow up.

485
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,880
For a shipyard,

486
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,510
having a safety accident

487
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:02,270
is perfectly normal.

488
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:13,160
We're in the same boat now.

489
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:14,920
What's the popular term for it?

490
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:17,070
Deeply bound.

491
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,920
Deeply bound.

492
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:20,270
What an accurate term.

493
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:28,210
You have to be ruthless,

494
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:30,440
and know how to leverage force.

495
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:32,640
If you trust me,

496
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:34,300
you can give me the materials.

497
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,240
Then those people who stopped Lu Ming

498
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,790
from being with me,

499
00:31:11,310 --> 00:31:12,710
where did they come from?

500
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:13,960
Xia Xue.

501
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,110
You're free.

502
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:26,200
Hello?

503
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:28,570
I am Mr. Ma's secretary.

504
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:30,510
Mr. Ma asked me to tell you

505
00:31:30,510 --> 00:31:32,680
that he's been taken away by the police.

506
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:34,160
Before he left, he said

507
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:35,920
he would be back very soon.

508
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:38,440
The guy who set him up is Uncle San's man,

509
00:31:38,590 --> 00:31:39,880
named Lu Ming.

510
00:31:40,830 --> 00:31:42,480
You know what to do, right?

511
00:31:55,510 --> 00:31:56,350
So,

512
00:31:58,000 --> 00:32:00,260
you were behind the shipyard explosion.

513
00:32:03,510 --> 00:32:04,920
You killed my father.

514
00:32:07,550 --> 00:32:09,480
And you forced Lu Ming to leave.

515
00:32:15,350 --> 00:32:16,160
Xia Xue.

516
00:32:22,790 --> 00:32:24,270
Did you ever love me?

517
00:32:41,790 --> 00:32:42,720
Actually,

518
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:47,720
Officer Qin Wen never gave me any button.

519
00:32:55,960 --> 00:32:58,240
It seems you really never loved me.

520
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,480
Xia Xue,

521
00:33:01,270 --> 00:33:03,240
do you really think I didn't know

522
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:04,680
all your little schemes?

523
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,790
I never exposed you

524
00:33:06,790 --> 00:33:09,030
because I was gambling.

525
00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:11,070
Gambling on our eight years together.

526
00:33:11,070 --> 00:33:13,400
Gambling on everything I gave you.

527
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,530
Gambling that you had me in your heart.

528
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:17,350
Looks like I lost.

529
00:33:21,310 --> 00:33:22,350
Fine.

530
00:33:24,550 --> 00:33:26,640
Then let's drop the act.

531
00:33:26,830 --> 00:33:28,720
I'll let you know right now

532
00:33:28,720 --> 00:33:30,030
who's

533
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:33,350
really controlling the game.

534
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:13,840
If you die,

535
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:16,230
your son can live a good life.

536
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:25,199
Do you know how

537
00:34:25,550 --> 00:34:26,810
to write a confession?

538
00:34:47,550 --> 00:34:49,760
One, two, three, freeze.

539
00:34:49,760 --> 00:34:50,880
No talking.

540
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:51,960
No moving.

541
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:59,570
Let me take your hair down for bed.

542
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:10,440
Long time no see, Chang.

543
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:18,590
Take Xia Xue to the abandoned villa
in Guanshan.

544
00:35:27,110 --> 00:35:29,190
Mr. Hou, it's done.

545
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:32,070
I'll give you the rest of the money
when it's over.

546
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:34,270
Okay, I'll wait for your good news then.

547
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:38,570
You're pretty good at fighting, huh?

548
00:35:48,710 --> 00:35:49,760
Let them go.

549
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:53,510
You can take my life.

550
00:35:54,030 --> 00:35:55,920
Chang, I didn't

551
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:57,800
want to get involved in this.

552
00:35:59,360 --> 00:36:03,400
But I really couldn't resist the money.

553
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,000
Biao!

554
00:36:05,230 --> 00:36:06,000
Biao.

555
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,000
Let Shanshan go.

556
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,760
Biao! Biao!

557
00:36:11,190 --> 00:36:11,920
Let's go!

558
00:36:14,550 --> 00:36:15,400
Let me go.

559
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:36,280
Actually,
during these ten years in prison,

560
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:38,010
I only thought about one thing.

561
00:36:38,840 --> 00:36:41,280
Who's behind all this

562
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:43,630
and sent me to prison?

563
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:46,800
I still need to uncover the truth

564
00:36:47,710 --> 00:36:49,440
about the shipyard explosion.

565
00:36:50,230 --> 00:36:51,630
But this case, you see,

